headline: Housing market: Affordability, earnings, top picks, & fresh data
summary: Mortgage rates continue to impact homebuyer affordability, with many buyers still on the sidelines. Market Domination co-host Josh Lipton joins Yahoo Finance Senior Reporter Allie Canal on Wealth to discuss the latest data and what investors should watch for, including opportunities in Beazer Homes (BZH), Toll Brothers (TOL), and PulteGroup (PHM). To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Wealth here.
